  <brief_title>Comparison of the Result of TVT Performed at the Time of Prolapse Surgery or 3 Months After</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter Prospective Randomized Trial Comparing to Strategies When Incontinence Surgery is Needed in Addition to Prolapse Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
